Job interview make-up 💄 
I had a job interview today and did my makeup like this. It is very simple and I did not want to create a heavy make-up look for the interview. I used soft tones. For my eyeshadow I used the soft glam palette by @anastasiabeverlyhills and anastasia brow kit for my eyebrows. For my lashes I used @rimmellondonuk and @nyxcosmetics eyeliner
